OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and clear. Then the rest
OL,7,Fof the night will be mostly dry but
OL,8,Fclouding over in south and west later
OL,9,Fwith the chance of the odd shower. A
OL,10,Fcold night with a frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy with a few showers
OL,13,Fspreading north through the morning,
OL,14,Fcontinuing into the afternoon.
OL,15,FGenerally drier in the east. Mild
OL,16,Facross Fife and the Central Belt.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
