OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fspreading east on Thursday afternoon,
OL,7,Fclearing early on Friday. Then Friday
OL,8,Fand Saturday will be dry with some
OL,9,Fbrightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
